text: Govinda Prasad Kalauni (Nepali: गोविन्दप्रसाद कलाैनी) is the current Governor of Karnali Province.He was appointed governor, under Article 163 of the Constitution of Nepal, by President Bidya Devi Bhandari on the recommendation of the Council of Ministers of the Government of Nepal on 4 November 2019. == References == Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Nepalese politicians Category:Governors of Provinces of Nepal
title: Govinda Prasad Kalauni
